[
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "是什么人鬼鬼祟祟地站在外面？快走！",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 42
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "明月心，是你？",
    "tone": "焦急",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 46
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我不认得你，你快走。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 50
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你不该这样闯进来的！你应该知道现在我是别人的妻子。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 62
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我已将卓玉贞送去了，你为什么还来找我？",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 66
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "因为你就是我要找的人，你就是明月心。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 68
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你错了。",
    "tone": "叹息",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 74
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "哦？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 76
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "世上根本没有明月心这样一个人，明月根本就是无心的。",
    "tone": "淡然",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 78
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "也许你以前的确在别的地方见过明月心，可是那个人也正像你以前的情人翠浓一样，已不存在了。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 84
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "只可惜你还是做错了一件事，你不该杀卓玉贞。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 90
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "你杀她，只因为你恨我。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 94
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "不错，我恨你，所以我希望你死。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 106
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
    "speaker_name": "老人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我知道你是夜眼，你一定已看出我是个老人。",
    "tone": "微笑",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 228
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_lao_ren",
    "text": "你也希望我击败公子羽？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 234
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
    "speaker_name": "老人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我至少不想你死。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 236
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_lao_ren",
    "text": "我活着对你有什么好处？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 238
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
    "speaker_name": "老人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "没有好处，我只希望这一战能真正公平。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 240
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_lao_ren",
    "text": "哦？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 242
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
    "speaker_name": "老人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "只有真正的强者得胜，这一战才算公平。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 244
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
    "speaker_name": "老人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "强者拥有一切，本是天经地义的事。也只有真正的强者才配得到这一切。",
    "tone": "庄严",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 250
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_lao_ren",
    "text": "你认为我比他强？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 254
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
    "speaker_name": "老人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "至少你是惟一有机会击败他的人，可是你现在太紧张，太疲倦。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 256
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
    "speaker_name": "老人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "现在距离你们的决斗还有八个时辰，你若不能使你自己完全松弛，明日此刻，你的尸体一定已冰冷。",
    "tone": "严肃",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 260
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
    "speaker_name": "老人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "从这里走出去，向右转三次，左边的一间房里，有个女人躺在床上等着你。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 264
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_lao_ren",
    "text": "谁？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 266
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
    "speaker_name": "老人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你用不着问她是谁，也不必知道她为什么要等你！",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 268
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
    "speaker_name": "老人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "像你这样的男人，本该将天下的女人当作工具。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 272
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_lao_ren",
    "text": "工具？",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 274
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
    "speaker_name": "老人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "她就是惟一可以让你松弛的工具。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 276
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
    "speaker_name": "老人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你若不这样做，出门后就向左转三次，也可以找到一间屋子。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 280
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_lao_ren",
    "text": "那屋里有什么？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 282
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
    "speaker_name": "老人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "棺材。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 284
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_lao_ren",
    "text": "你究竟是什么人？凭什么来命令我？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 286
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你是谁？为什么要等我？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 328
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你知道我是谁？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 336
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你已准备好了？",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 375
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "好，你跟我来。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 379
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "现在你若想逃走，我还可以指点你一条出路。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 391
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你是否已决定放弃？",
    "tone": "冷静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 425
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "放弃什么？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 427
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "放弃选择见证的权利！",
    "tone": "冷静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 429
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "我只想找一个人。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 431
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "谁？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 433
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "一个铁柜中的老人。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 435
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我不知道你说的是谁。",
    "tone": "冷静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 437
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "那么我放弃。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 439
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "既然如此，就只好让我找的六个人来做见证了。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 441
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "很好。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 443
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "第一个人就是我，你反不反对？",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 445
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "第二位是陈大老板。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 449
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_chen_da_lao_ban",
    "text": "你当然是认得这位陈大老板的。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 459
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_chen_da_lao_ban",
    "text": "这位陈大老板也认得你。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 461
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chen_da_lao_ban",
    "speaker_name": "陈大老板",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我认得，一年前我们就已在凤凰集上见过面。",
    "tone": "恐惧",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 465
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_chen_da_lao_ban",
    "text": "你们很熟？",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 475
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chen_da_lao_ban",
    "speaker_name": "陈大老板",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "不能算很熟，左右只见过一次面。",
    "tone": "恐惧",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 477
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_chen_da_lao_ban",
    "text": "只见过一次，你就记得！",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 479
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chen_da_lao_ban",
    "speaker_name": "陈大老板",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "因为自从这位客官到过小店后，小店就毁了，凤凰集也毁了，我……",
    "tone": "恐惧",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 481
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_chen_da_lao_ban",
    "text": "我们到那边去坐。留得青山在，不怕没柴烧，过去了的事，你也不必再放在心上。",
    "tone": "温柔",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 487
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chen_da_lao_ban",
    "speaker_name": "陈大老板",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "我不……不会……",
    "tone": "恐惧",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 489
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "陈老板不但老实敦厚，而且见多识广，做见证正是再好也没有的了！",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 495
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "是。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 497
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "第三位是藏珍阁的主人倪宝峰倪老先生。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 501
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "倪老先生是武林前辈，不但认宝，而且识人。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 513
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "我知道。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 515
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "能够请到倪老先生来做我们的见证，实在是我们的荣幸。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 517
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "是。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 519
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我请来这三位见证你都不反对？",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 521
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "高手相争，正如国手对弈，一着之失，满盘皆输，所以连心情都受不得半点影响。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 525
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "我知道。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 527
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "他们都没有影响你？",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 529
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "没有。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 531
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "第四位是九华山的如意大师。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line": 541
  }
]